description: Jack and Riley sure know how to swing their bats. They warm up on the baseball diamond, prepping for a ball-filled day. “We’re about to get know each other really well,” says Jack. “I’m excited to see what the day entails for us.” “We got a little pump in, a little workout playing some baseball,” says Riley. “I got him ready. I don’t want to wear him out later.” “I’m going to have to you up a couple times I think,” says Jack. “Well I definitely like being pushed around,” responds Riley.
title: Jack & Riley: Bareback
